Welcome to the Homestuck Community Survey 2020! Before you start, here are some notes:
- THIS SURVEY IS NOT OFFICIAL!!! This project is being conducted by a group of Homestuck fans. What Pumpkin and Snake Solutions are NOT involved with the organization, creation, proofreading, or wording of this survey. Andrew Hussie and Aysha U. Farah are not affiliated with this survey.
- This survey is an attempt to understand the perspectives and makeup of the Homestuck community in 2020. We encourage anyone who considers themself part of this community to respond!
- You can respond from July 10 to August 10. After that, the survey will be closed for analysis.
- No questions are required. You can skip over whatever you don't know or want to answer.
- Please click through all the way to the end and click the blue "submit" button for your responses to be counted.
Thank you so much for your help!
